%p Hey #{@user.first_name_or_fallback},

%p
  Read-only MCP access was just enabled for your Dabble Me account (#{@user.email}).
  If you turned this on, you can ignore this message.

%p
  MCP connections use a separate secret token (shown only once when you generate it) and expire after six months unless you generate a new token.
  For Claude custom connectors, paste the full URL from your MCP settings page (it includes
  %code access_token=
  in the query string).

%p
  If you did not enable MCP,
  = link_to "sign in", new_user_session_url
  and revoke access from your
  = succeed "." do
    = link_to "MCP settings", settings_mcp_url

%p
  %br
  Thanks,
  %br
  Dabble Me
